<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>
  <main>
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <div class="faq-container">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="faq1">
        <label for="faq1" class="faq-question">How do I enroll in a course?</label>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>To enroll, visit the Courses page, select a course, and follow the registration link provided. Youâ€™ll need to create an account and complete the enrollment form.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="faq2">
        <label for="faq2" class="faq-question">Are live sessions recorded?</label>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes, most live sessions are recorded and available for registered students to access on the platform for a limited time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="faq3">
        <label for="faq3" class="faq-question">How can I contact an instructor?</label>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Instructor contact details are listed on the Instructors page. You can also submit queries via the Contact Us form.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <input type="checkbox" id="faq4">
        <label for="faq4" class="faq-question">What are the technical requirements?</label>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>You need a modern browser (Chrome, Firefox, or Edge) and a stable internet connection. No additional software is required.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>